---
layout: layout.njk
lang: en
title: "Yuulia — AI Process Automation Consultancy"
description: "Yuulia is an AI process automation consultancy for companies of any size and sector. Free 30-minute process audit, no strings attached."
ogDescription: "AI process automation with human oversight, for companies of any size and sector. The final decision always belongs to your team."
permalink: /en/
---
<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow rise">Technology consultancy · Spain</p>
  <h1 class="rise-1">We automate your company's processes with artificial intelligence.</h1>
  <div class="hero-grid rise-2">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-lead">We design AI agents that classify, prepare and leave the work ready for review. In any sector, at any scale. The final decision always belongs to your team.</p>
      <p class="impact-chip"><strong>~9 h/week recovered</strong> on average across repetitive processes · illustrative estimate</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn-primary">Request a free audit</a>
      <p class="hint">30 minutes · no strings attached · we tell you if it is not worth it</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ VIDEO ============ -->
<section class="visual-break">
  <div class="visual-break-wrap">
    <div class="visual-break-media">
      <video
        class="visual-break-video"
        poster="/assets/images/video-poster.jpg"
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        preload="metadata"
        aria-label="Yuulia presentation video. On-screen text is in Spanish; there is no spoken narration.">
        <source src="/assets/videos/yuulia-presentacion.webm" type="video/webm">
        <source src="/assets/videos/yuulia-presentacion.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      </video>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="visual-break-caption">
    <details class="visual-break-transcript">
      <summary>Transcript (translated from Spanish)</summary>
      <p>Every company has the same silent problem. Not in deciding. In repeating. Yuulia takes care of the repetitive. You decide what matters. Nothing is decided alone. Everything goes through someone on your team. The time you gain is time for what only your team knows how to do. Yuulia.</p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ THE PROBLEM ============ -->
<section id="solucion" class="labeled-section">
  <p class="eyebrow">The problem</p>
  <div>
    <h2 class="section-title">The hidden cost of repetitive work.</h2>
    <div class="problema-grid">
      <div class="problema-card">
        {% icon "bandeja" %}
        <p class="tag">In a professional firm</p>
        <p class="body">Sorting every enquiry and finding its case file before being able to reply.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problema-card">
        {% icon "recibo" %}
        <p class="tag">In a restaurant</p>
        <p class="body">Invoices arriving as WhatsApp photos, copied by hand into the cost sheet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problema-card">
        {% icon "etiqueta" %}
        <p class="tag">In a retail business</p>
        <p class="body">The same product listing, uploaded again to every platform.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="problema-close">None of this requires judgement. An agent takes it on and your team gets 2 to 4 hours back every day.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ HOW WE WORK ============ -->
<section id="proceso" class="labeled-section">
  <p class="eyebrow">How we work</p>
  <div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Four steps, in this order.</h2>
    <div>
      <div class="paso">
        {% icon "lupa" %}
        <span class="num">1</span>
        <h3>We audit before touching anything.</h3>
        <p>One week measuring where the time goes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="paso">
        {% icon "plano" %}
        <span class="num">2</span>
        <h3>We design the agent with you.</h3>
        <p>What it reads, what it prepares and what it never decides on its own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="paso">
        {% icon "borrador" %}
        <span class="num">3</span>
        <h3>It starts in draft mode.</h3>
        <p>Everything goes through your team until it earns trust.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="paso">
        {% icon "grafico-barras" %}
        <span class="num">4</span>
        <h3>We measure the real savings.</h3>
        <p>A monthly report of hours recovered. If it is not worth it, we stop.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ WHY YUULIA ============ -->
<section id="por-que" class="labeled-section">
  <p class="eyebrow">Why Yuulia</p>
  <div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Real engineering, not pretty demos.</h2>
    <ul class="diferenciales">
      <li>
        {% icon "escudo" %}
        <div>
          <h3>Robust from day one</h3>
          <p>Error handling, retries and alerts. An agent that fails silently is worse than no agent at all.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        {% icon "grafico-barras" %}
        <div>
          <h3>Real monitoring</h3>
          <p>You see what each agent did and why. No black boxes.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        {% icon "usuarios" %}
        <div>
          <h3>Direct contact</h3>
          <p>You talk to the person who builds your agent, with no intermediaries.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ SECTORS ============ -->
<section id="sectores" class="labeled-section">
  <p class="eyebrow">Sectors</p>
  <div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Experience in your sector, whatever it is.</h2>
    <div class="sectores-grid">
      <div class="sector">
        {% icon "maletin" %}
        <h3>Professional firms</h3>
        <p>The inbox sorts itself and invoices are registered without typing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sector">
        {% icon "cubiertos" %}
        <h3>Hospitality</h3>
        <p>Invoices reconciled however they arrive, and orders adjusted to real consumption.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sector">
        {% icon "bolsa" %}
        <h3>Retail</h3>
        <p>Catalogue and stock up to date across all your sales platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sector">
        {% icon "llave-inglesa" %}
        <h3>Field services</h3>
        <p>Work reports and quotes ready for review, straight from the phone.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="problema-close">Your sector is not on the list? It makes no difference. If a repetitive process exists, an agent can take it on.</p>
    <div class="section-cta">
      <a href="#contacto" class="btn-primary">Book an audit →</a>
      <p class="hint">30 minutes · no strings attached</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ REFERENCE FIGURES ============ -->
<section id="cifras" class="stats-band">
  <div class="stats-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">Reference figures</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What tends to happen when automation is done well.</h2>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-tile">
        {% icon "reloj" %}
        <span class="stat-num">2-4 h</span>
        <span class="stat-label">freed per day across the processes we audit</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-tile">
        {% icon "porcentaje" %}
        <span class="stat-num">60-70%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">of routine enquiries resolved without human intervention</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-tile">
        {% icon "calendario" %}
        <span class="stat-num">1-2 wks</span>
        <span class="stat-label">to get your first agent running in draft mode</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-tile">
        {% icon "candado" %}
        <span class="stat-num">100%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">of outputs reviewed by a person while trust is earned</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="stats-disclaimer">Industry reference figures, not a promise. The free audit calculates the real number for your business.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<section id="preguntas" class="labeled-section">
  <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
  <div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Clear answers.</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Does the agent replace my team?</summary>
        <p>No. It takes on the repetitive work so your team can focus on what adds value. The final decision always goes through a person.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I have to change my tools?</summary>
        <p>No. We build the agent on top of what you already use: your email, your management software, your spreadsheets.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How much does it cost?</summary>
        <p>It depends on the scope. The 30-minute audit is free and gives you an estimate of the savings before you invest in anything.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How long until it is up and running?</summary>
        <p>A basic agent, 1 to 2 weeks. More complete systems, 4 to 8.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What happens to my data?</summary>
        <p>We work with self-hosted options and GDPR compliance where the case requires it. We review it together before touching anything sensitive.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CTA ============ -->
<section id="contacto" class="cta">
  <div class="cta-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow">First step</p>
    <h2>A 30-minute call. You leave knowing what to automate.</h2>
    <p>We tell you what deserves an agent and what does not. If it is not worth it, we say so too.</p>
    <!-- TODO: activar Email Routing en Cloudflare para que info@yuulia.com reciba correo -->
    <a href="mailto:info@yuulia.com?subject=Process%20audit" class="btn-dark">Book an audit →</a>
    <p class="hint">30 minutes · no strings attached · we tell you if it is not worth it</p>
  </div>
</section>

